      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Subject: Formal Notice: Urgent Attention Required for Punctuality Issues\n\nDear [Employee's Name],\n\nI trust this message finds you well. I am writing to formally address a matter that has been consistently observed and requires immediate attention. Over the past two weeks, it has been noted that your arrival times have been consistently delayed by approximately 15 minutes on several occasions.\n\nI understand that unforeseen circumstances can sometimes cause delays, but it is imperative that we maintain a consistent work schedule to ensure the smooth operation of our team and the overall productivity of our organization. Late arrivals can disrupt the workflow, affect the performance of your colleagues, and ultimately impact the quality of service we provide to our clients.\n\nThis matter is of serious concern, and as such, I must issue a formal warning. Punctuality is a valued trait in our workplace, and it is expected of all employees to adhere to their scheduled start times. Failure to do so may result in disciplinary action, which could include a formal review of your employment status.\n\nI urge you to take this warning seriously and make a concerted effort to improve your punctuality moving forward. If there are any underlying issues that are causing these delays, please do not hesitate to discuss them with me. I",
